body_html:
Looks like homebrew only has protobuf up to 3.0
http://brewformulas.org/Protobuf
Our pip packages require protobuf 3.1, and we are upgrading to 3.2.
Maybe we should recommend against using homebrew installed protobuf?

@jhseu wdyt?
